\begin_inset Formula $\mu_{T}\left(x\right)=1$
\end_inset

 corresponding to the Frobenius-Perron eigenvalue of the transfer operator:
 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathcal{L}_{T}\mu_{T}=\mu_{T}$
\end_inset

.
